O '''Themesko Dives vash o Poraimosko Astaripen pe Godyate''' si ekh baro dives andi [[Rumuniya]], pe [[9 Oktobra]], prinjardo kashte anel pe godyate o [[Poraimos]] thai o [[Shoa]] andar o [[Duito Lumyako Maripen]]. Sas alosardo kadava dives anda kodoya so sas o ekhto dives ([[1942]]to bersh) kana le [[Yehudurya]] (Zhidovurya) sas bichhalde kai [[Transnistriya]]. Divesardo po ekhtule ando [[2004]]to bersh. 

Pe 9 Oktobra [[2006]], varesave [[Roma]] manglen te prinjarel pes chaches vi o Romengo Poraimos andi Rumuniya, te lekhavel/ramol pe late ande siklyovnenge lila <ref name="reuters2006">[http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L09244938.htm Le Rumunurya chi prinjaren chaches o Poraimos (anglezikanes)], Reuters, 9 Oktobra, 2006</ref>.

